text: Anastasiya Dzedzikava (born 2 January 1997) is a Belarusian professional racing cyclist. She signed to ride for the UCI Women's Team for the 2019 women's road cycling season, but left midway through the season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
